PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Analysis App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is this app used for?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides powerful analytics and insights into new blockchain data as it gets added to the ledger. It helps you stay on top of the latest transactions, contracts, and activities happening on the blockchain.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We utilize advanced algorithms and machine learning models to parse and interpret the raw blockchain data. Our app then surfaces key metrics, trends, and anomalies that you can easily explore and monitor.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Currently we support analysis for Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchain networks. We are constantly working to add support for more blockchains based on user demand.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, we offer a 30-day free trial so you can test out the full capabilities of our blockchain analysis app before subscribing. Sign up today to get started!
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our blockchain data analysis platform
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of blockchain data can be analyzed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our platform can analyze data from major blockchains like Bitcoin, Ethereum, and others. We support on-chain data, transaction data, smart contract data, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How is the data collected and stored?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We utilize decentralized node infrastructure to directly collect data from blockchains in a trustless manner. Data is stored in a distributed database for high availability.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What kinds of analyses can be performed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Popular analyses include token metrics, network analytics, smart contract auditing, and anomaly detection. Custom analyses can also be built using our APIs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How can I access the analysis tools?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: You can access our web dashboard, use our APIs and SDKs, or integrate our data streams directly into your apps and workflows.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, our team of blockchain experts can provide consulting, custom development, and training services tailored to your needs.
